{"tid":2489631,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"依賴贊助 換品牌憂重創奧運成績  疆棉風暴體壇取態曖昧 國足照穿NIKE出賽","createTime":"2021-04-15T05:10:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T05:20:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8dcb796492a49d121371f7eda8f37a6415cb2df6","tid":2489631,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T05:10:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210415/OXMU4L7RBBFZ3MW4FZEVVUJOHQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210415%2FOXMU4L7RBBFZ3MW4FZEVVUJOHQ%2F&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sOIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=47224fd4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210415%2FOXMU4L7RBBFZ3MW4FZEVVUJOHQ%2F&h=f8f6d773\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210415/OXMU4L7RBBFZ3MW4FZEVVUJOHQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n依賴贊助 換品牌憂重創奧運成績 <br />\n疆棉風暴體壇取態曖昧 國足照穿NIKE出賽<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】東京奧運距今不足百日。惟對於NIKE等捲入新疆棉風波的體育用品品牌，中國體育界卻態度曖昧，包括中國國家足球隊等，均未有與該些品牌斷絕合作。直到前日（13日）東京奧運會女足預選賽，國家隊球員仍身穿NIKE球衣出戰。有內地知名體育評論人直言，中國運動員極度依賴有關品牌提供的裝備，若臨時換裝，將嚴重影響東京奧運成績。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：日食品商KAGOME停用新疆番茄<br />\n<br />\n內地民間持續抵制拒用新疆棉的海外品牌，對於作為中國國家足球隊球衣贊助商的NIKE等，不少網民亦呼籲解約，但除有中超球隊遮蓋球衣上有關品牌商標，及足協內部會議譴責外，體育界至今未積極參與杯葛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/syi8l4W3uOnvNBgzAxV9e1XS53g=/510x340/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IPNC4HEMARGKPEY3KRMKGEDJNY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fsyi8l4W3uOnvNBgzAxV9e1XS53g%3D%2F510x340%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIPNC4HEMARGKPEY3KRMKGEDJNY.jpg&h=4410c42c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■多個國際品牌拒用涉強迫維人勞動生產的新疆棉花。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n合約逾11億 割席料巨額賠償<br />\n<br />\n奧運會女子足球項目前日舉行亞洲區預選賽附加賽，中國隊球員身上穿着的球衣仍是NIKE贊助。此外，男、女籃球國家隊隊及田徑國家隊，NIKE亦是主要贊助商。當紅男籃名將易建聯、郭艾倫等，亦為該品牌代言人。<br />\n<br />\n其中，國足與NIKE簽訂12年合約，價值10億元人民幣（約11.87億港元）。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n國際品牌贊助佔據中國體壇半壁江山，其提供的裝備更對中國隊表現有關鍵影響。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n香港浸會大學體育學系副教授雷雄。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n雙方簽訂的協議書內必然會列明提早解約的條件。國家隊倘要在奧運會前與NIKE或adidas等割席，除非雙方同意，否則就需要賠償。<br />\n<br />\n專注日本研究的台灣國立政治大學教授李世暉分析，東京奧運時中國隊或。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oAa8HC3pcQdgjIee6Rz4zHl4gNM=/510x340/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/74JI2D7BP5EYJFYMIFV3W3J5YA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoAa8HC3pcQdgjIee6Rz4zHl4gNM%3D%2F510x340%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F74JI2D7BP5EYJFYMIFV3W3J5YA.jpg&h=b3316d54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中國女足前日出戰南韓隊時，仍穿NIKE球衣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Ta3IDffIugGD7_CkxFSvoXi0Lb0=/510x510/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VWW3GPPWVNBMFKIWEBMDSA6P7Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTa3IDffIugGD7_CkxFSvoXi0Lb0%3D%2F510x510%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVWW3GPPWVNBMFKIWEBMDSA6P7Q.jpg&h=428a680e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■國家田徑隊選手蘇炳添的NIKE田徑鞋，對其表現有關鍵影響。"},{"pid":"f4ab1e9834e08c6ef7690b9a1a78991927327ef8","tid":2489631,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T05:12:26.000Z","msg":"支足又變condom <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dafed90cc1edd2ed2aad0cc4f848db27f71b292","tid":2489631,"uid":7860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T05:12:35.000Z","msg":"單春成最大輸家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e918b6c6cf7547d075d859dee774928698da8d0","tid":2489631,"uid":173921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T05:13:06.000Z","msg":"支那啲垃圾鞋唔著斷啲人隻腳都偷笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db92b259c340402cc05ad2f09d70db176c6d0d6","tid":2489631,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T05:14:22.000Z","msg":"唔著Nike=影響成績<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2fd583b62c24dd9d78a474bdaf4f1cb567868c","tid":2489631,"uid":52122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dafed90cc1edd2ed2aad0cc4f848db27f71b292","tid":2489631,"uid":7860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T05:12:35.000Z","msg":"單春成最大輸家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T05:14:48.000Z","msg":"呢條友真係最on9<br />\n自己份約咁撚大 咁撚衝動去毁約柒撚到"},{"pid":"f1b2a9208807d5a8dcaa2f6b946cda8f1212a217","tid":2489631,"uid":57674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1db92b259c340402cc05ad2f09d70db176c6d0d6","tid":2489631,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T05:14:22.000Z","msg":"唔著Nike=影響成績<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T05:18:17.000Z","msg":"著NIKE會差左<br />\n中國唔想贏太多落人面"},{"pid":"c783fd2e10975ea79aac14706801203571e001bd","tid":2489631,"uid":128873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T05:20:50.000Z","msg":"中國人唔著返自己牌子太掉架了<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}